page.title: 04I LIVE IN HUNNINGHAM (CONT.)
page.content: In the garage lots of things are kept; wood, the car, the freezer and lots more. Most of it is my dad's. I have only got my bike and a few things in the car and my bucket and spade. {Shopping} is easy. My mum works in {Leamington}so she can shop in places in and around Leamington. There is a { {Post Office} near our village and it sells lots of things. I go to{Brownies}on Monday night in {Cubbington}. Me and my sister Amy sometimes have friends to come and play with us.When it is their birthday,we are sometimes invited to their parties. Me and my sister and mum and dad just run a normal life really.
